

** Memory

  > 1024 MB

** Appearance

Create a customized theme with "Clearlooks". "Ambiance" and "Radiance"
cause emacs to display a warning message.

** Oracle 11gR2

  - sysctl.pl and edit afterwards /etc/sysctl.conf
  - see RedhatOel

*** Additional Packages

  - libaio1
  - libaio-dev
  - sysstat
  - libelf-dev
  - unixodbc
  - unixodbc-dev
  - pdksh

*** Problems

  - dg4odbc
  - ctxhx
  - agtctl
  - extproc

** awk link

  - ln -s /usr/bin/awk /bin/awk

